---
title: Sheet Pan Dukkah Chicken with Carrots, Chickpeas and Lemony Kale
description: Exotic Dukkah spice combines nuts, spices and herbs to create a delicious crust on tender chicken in tonight's one-pan wonder. Lemony kale adds both bright and healthy notes for those of you keeping count!

